author: The Virginian-Pilot
title: Soccer | UTEP women end ODU's winning streak
text:
EL PASO, Texas Texas-El Paso scored twice in the first half and once in the second in a 3-0 Conference USA victory over Old Dominion.
The Lady Monarchs (7-10, 5-3), who had won three in a row, travel to Marshall at 7 p.m. Friday.
